urlhtml: The Archeological Crypt of the Parvis of Notre-Dame
title: The Archeological Crypt of the Parvis of Notre-Dame
description:
Entrance to the underground museum where Roman & medieval ruins are preserved. The area was excavated in the 1960's when the buildings in front of the Notre Dame cathedral were torn down to make way for the plaza.
